[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### N2. The `heart_score` rule's risk-strata interpretation in the Python (4-6 = moderate_risk → `emergency_department`) does not match the recipe's sample audit record (score=6 → high_risk → emergency_evaluation)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
